        },
        {
            "title": "20大屋苑估價九成上升｜康怡花園升約6%居首｜藍灣半島、碧海藍天按月未有變動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據28Hse最新追蹤的20個指標屋苑*數據，4月份二手物業的銀行估價普遍向好。滙豐銀行的資料顯示，大型及中型單位均有18個屋苑估價按月上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當中，<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鰂魚涌康怡花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:鰂魚涌康怡花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鰂魚涌康怡花園</a>的估價升幅最顯著，大型及中型單位分別按月上調6.08%及5.98%，分別位居大型及中型單位升幅榜首。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"20大屋苑估價八成上升｜青衣盈翠半島表現突出 升逾4%｜九龍及新界東指標屋苑估價輕微跌\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:20大屋苑估價八成上升｜青衣盈翠半島表現突出 升逾4%｜九龍及新界東指標屋苑估價輕微跌;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/415s22f\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">20大屋苑估價八成上升｜青衣盈翠半島表現突出 升逾4%｜九龍及新界東指標屋苑估價輕微跌</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"匯豐估價進取：銀行商業策略掛帥｜準買家宜在虛實間求平衡\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:匯豐估價進取：銀行商業策略掛帥｜準買家宜在虛實間求平衡;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4lcZgGa\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">匯豐估價進取：銀行商業策略掛帥｜準買家宜在虛實間求平衡</a></p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-51067af8-4108-3163-8087-503c06d428da-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FDvnNZmwg_R25wS6zfK0Sw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/eb0079bdf3f9a36013ececa9724e1909\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>20大屋苑4月估價排名 (大型單位)</strong></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>18個屋苑大型單位估價上調 康怡花園升6.08%居首</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4月大型單位估價普遍上升，20個指標屋苑中有18個錄得按月升幅，升幅介乎0.46%至6.08%。其中，<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"小西灣藍灣半島\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:小西灣藍灣半島;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4tkIBDb\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">小西灣藍灣半島</a>及<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荔枝角碧海藍天\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:荔枝角碧海藍天;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4rV6Rf4\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">荔枝角碧海藍天</a>則按月持平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>康怡花園升幅最大 滙豐估價升至1100萬</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滙豐估價顯示，升幅最大的屋苑為<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鰂魚涌康怡花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:鰂魚涌康怡花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鰂魚涌康怡花園</a>，以A座24樓4室為例，實用面積710平方呎，本月估價達1,100萬元，按月增加63萬元，升幅達6.08%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中銀及28Hse對同一單位的估價分別為1,070萬元及1,080.4萬元，按月分別上升3.08%及1.31%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇康怡花園放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇康怡花園放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇康怡花園放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>海怡半島升幅居次 滙豐估價升4.17%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">升幅第二大的屋苑為<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"南區海怡半島\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:南區海怡半島;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4jtM8vl\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">南區海怡半島</a>，以第3期17座（美暉閣）16樓E室為例，實用面積871平方呎，其滙豐估價由3月的1,343萬元升至本月的1,399萬元，按月升4.17%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中銀及28Hse對該單位的估價分別為1,443萬元及1,400.5萬元，按月分別持平及下跌0.65%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇海怡半島放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇海怡半島放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4jtM8vl\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇海怡半島放盤】</a></p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://i1.28hse.com/2026/04/202604021745512162102_large_nowm.jpg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Kvv4y0eUMgm_SbMXLb1E8g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/458527feaa182b1a908bf9c7fb1ac89d\" width=\"320\"/></div></a><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://i1.28hse.com/2026/04/20260402174556461898_large_nowm.jpg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FNe3gPFftJ0vYI0u53PVWw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/c9a76ca7a64110d3deeaba890f0836e6\" width=\"320\"/></div></a><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://i1.28hse.com/2026/04/202604021746036251915_large_nowm.jpg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RlziUza7FaC4k0_HDnMF3A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/444a47f90ee0b6b8a782afaff8063e2c\" width=\"320\"/></div></a><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"+17\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:+17;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://i1.28hse.com/2026/04/202604021746036251915_large_nowm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">  +17 </a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>中型單位走勢相若 康怡花園按月升5.98%居首</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4月中型單位估價走勢與大型單位相若，20個指標屋苑中同樣有18個錄得按月升幅，升幅介乎0.47%至5.98%。<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"小西灣藍灣半島\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:小西灣藍灣半島;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4tkIBDb\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">小西灣藍灣半島</a>及<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荔枝角碧海藍天\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:荔枝角碧海藍天;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4rV6Rf4\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">荔枝角碧海藍天</a>的估價則按月維持不變。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RTxkdH6TBb27UelEvnkKiw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/9d1664909481aeb498211fd44c314ed8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>20大屋苑4月估價排名 (中型單位)</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>康怡花園升幅最多 滙豐估價升至727萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">升幅最大的屋苑同樣為<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"鰂魚涌康怡花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:鰂魚涌康怡花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鰂魚涌康怡花園</a>。滙豐估價顯示，P座11樓9室，實用面積490平方呎，4月估價為727萬元，較上月增加41萬元，按月上升5.98%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中銀及28Hse對同一單位的估價分別為675萬元及702.2萬元，按月分別上升3.05%及1.24%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇康怡花園放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇康怡花園放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3McZEHA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇康怡花園放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>荃威花園緊隨其後 滙豐估價按月升4.25%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">升幅第二大的屋苑為<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荃灣荃威花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:荃灣荃威花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4aFML2B\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">荃灣荃威花園</a>，以B座23樓2室為例，實用面積457平方呎，滙豐估價由3月的353萬元升至4月的368萬元，按月上升4.25%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中銀及28Hse對該單位的估價分別為388萬元及362.8萬元，按月分別上升1.04%及下跌0.58%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇荃威花園放盤】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇荃威花園放盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4aFML2B\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇荃威花園放盤】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">整體而言，4月20個指標屋苑的估價普遍向上，反映銀行對二手住宅估值較上月略為積極。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>市場氣氛向好 銀行估價普遍上調</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場人士認為，4月估價普遍上升，主要反映3月住宅市場交投大致平穩，銀行估價亦跟隨近期成交有所調整。由於估價一般參考土地註冊處紀錄及同類單位成交，當市場價格回穩，估價通常會逐步反映。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月一手市場表現亦不差，部分中小型新盤首輪銷售反應理想，例如瑧玥及瑜意均成功沽清，對整體樓市氣氛有支持，亦帶動二手市場表現。據香港置業資料顯示，3月住宅物業註冊量錄6,763宗，較2月的7,037宗輕微回落約3.9%，但仍屬近23個月第二高，反映住宅交投大致維持活躍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇瑧玥價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇瑧玥價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3N3VYrT\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇瑧玥價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇瑜意價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇瑜意價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3Nre2MP\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇瑜意價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>政策及按揭因素利好市場氣氛</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政策方面，2月底公布的《財政預算案》上調逾1億元住宅交易的印花稅，但政府估計僅影響約0.3%住宅成交，對主流屋苑影響輕微。因此，近期估價上調，主要反映二手市場氣氛改善，以及銀行按最新成交修訂估值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，金管局與業界自2月28日起將物業交易付款安排擴展至二手住宅市場，有助令交易流程更為順暢。加上市場仍預期美國年內或會減息，而3月下旬與樓按相關的1個月香港銀行同業拆息（HIBOR）曾報1.95厘，創1個月新低，亦有助維持買家入市意欲。銀行在參考最新成交及市場環境後，對部分主流屋苑的估價取態亦較早前進取。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">*20個指標屋苑包括：太古城、康怡花園、海怡半島、嘉亨灣、藍灣半島、寶翠園、南豐新邨、映灣園、嘉湖山莊、沙田第一城、新都城、新港城、珀麗灣、盈翠半島、荃威花園、美孚新邨、麗港城、德福花園、碧海藍天及黃埔花園</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"瑧玥\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:瑧玥;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/瑧玥\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">瑧玥</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"瑜意\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:瑜意;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/瑜意\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">瑜意</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"沙田第一城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:沙田第一城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/沙田第一城-4080\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">沙田第一城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"德福花園\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:德福花園;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/德福花園-2080\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">德福花園</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"嘉湖山莊\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:嘉湖山莊;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/嘉