            "title": "中東火藥桶再燃，恐慌指數飆升7%！美指期貨重挫1%，原油大升7%，幣圈超15萬人爆倉",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，4月2日，特朗普在講話中表示，美國將在\"未來兩到三周\"對伊朗展開更猛烈的打擊。美股開市前，CBOE Volatility Index飆升7%，美股指期貨重挫約1%，納指100期貨跌300點，跌幅達1.41%，道指30期貨跌逾400點，跌幅達1.41%，標普500期貨跌1.09%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"196\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/B5.lT5REDZCjmeytaGejDw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE5Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/771cd5419d3347c8574860682dc126fa\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">XAU/USD跌超2%失守4700美元大關，XAG/USD大跌4%至71美元。原油反彈大升約7%，倫敦布倫特原油期貨重返108美元；WTI原油期貨升至106.7美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cbc7d869-a070-3d97-84b2-65313f4db268-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"652\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lsyPGg1v4TpNQOGPXHhhxg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMjI-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/6f5321e6554399278d75c166b3cf23ac\" width=\"558\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">避險情緒升溫推動美元指數走高，重回100整數關口上方。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"574\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pbeLBpUe7m.BNWwyDfS0.g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/15ab602c3df3e8aaa2e0b4b5fd03dc38\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">風險資產全線回落，比特幣 (BitfinexUSD)下挫3%，跌至6.6萬美元。Coinglass數據顯示，最近24小時，加密貨幣市場超15萬人爆倉，爆倉金額達3.53億美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"577\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VvaaZm5.73CpHUcOPAz6WA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/af8af3fcc2ecebb470ca1140e381e4b3\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>4</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月最新</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股嚟咗啦！邊啲個股有入選？依家訂閱</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>唔好錯過啦</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"480\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vO0RWHjWIT.qrj8DTmC7Uw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/170123a654142ba6b41a8d99710cd0b3\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p></blockquote></div>",
